---
title: Pork Agrodolce with Roasted Potatoes and Tenderstem® Broccoli
description: Agrodolce is a sticky sauce that comes from Italian cuisine, with "agro" meaning sour and "dolce" meaning sweet. Our version uses tomatoes and parsley to bring freshness to make this dish a more summery take on a classic dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R42_W16_UK_HVP19395-4_Main_low-344dcb17.jpg
